snippet.title: Scuba Dive ZX Spectrum (c) 1983 Durell Software
snippet.description: Explore the world beneath the waves in this excellent Spectrum adventure game by Mike A. Richardson. The real scuba diving only on ZX Spectrum! Don't forget your oxygen, this world is huge and deep.
